#### Description

This dashboard provides detailed visibility into user and system activity within the Nozomi Networks platform using the Audit data stream. 

It displays audit events by action type and controller to highlight the most common operations and their associated modules. Visualizations also include browser usage distribution, trends of audit activity over time, and actions grouped by user to support behavior analysis. A table lists the top 10 source IP addresses to help identify frequent origin points for system access. A saved search provides essential audit details including timestamp, event name, action, browser, username, controller, and IP address to support auditing, investigations, and compliance tracking.

**[Integration Page](/app/integrations/detail/nozomi_networks/overview)**
